// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2746 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: b2114bc0-bfef-5a0b-bd1f-cc23d8865762

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*alpine edge:*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*wolfi:*")
